 *** Terraform installation******
 
1. apt-get update

2. apt-get install wget unzip

3. wget https://releases.hashicorp.com/terraform/0.11.13/terraform_0.11.13_linux_amd64.zip

4. unzip ./terraform_0.11.13_linux_amd64.zip -d /usr/local/bin/

Ref url:  https://linoxide.com/linux-how-to/how-to-install-terraform-on-centos-ubuntu/